{"tid":349140,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【一周必看】 金鐘正義男：盡量幫人","createTime":"2017-08-06T10:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T18:27:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6be4e46757fc774c397b8d8655e648491fcc29","tid":349140,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170806/20112969\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170806%2F20112969&d=qmBGhWIfcDOk6vQx21bcvMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=cdd54b0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170806%2F20112969&h=0961c145\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170806/20112969</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】<br />\n金鐘正義男：盡量幫人<br />\n<br />\n5,906<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n港鐵荃灣綫連續3日故障，上周五傍晚金鐘站更引發兩名男子涉嫌打架被捕事件，當時有市民拍下一名正義男挺身力阻當中一名疑犯逃走的片段，事件成為網上熱話。《蘋果》接觸到獲封「正義男神」的Edward，他自言「本性衝動，但會帶住冷靜去解決問題」，今次事件是「希望喺能力之內幫到有需要嘅人」。<br />\n<br />\n近日成為網絡紅人、被封正義男神的青年自稱Edward，在港島區一間酒店任職工程，他謙稱網民對他的留言都抬舉了，對個人背景他不願多談，只透露是一名九十後青年。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【一周必看】建制議員去高鐵車廠　邊個令攝記笑得瘋狂？<br />\n下一則<br />\n【一周必看】動主播遭白兵生擒　試打VR新Game嚇餐懵"},{"pid":"d6d1fd24f1968e6e921b3dc2da0bb20013151b18","tid":349140,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好波"},{"pid":"5fbda6d0ad4862aaaa458878fa5fe91d9d0b6dae","tid":349140,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 